{"tid":302402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖睇到就來跌出來!!!) 陳瀅玩插沙　大汗到甩Bra","createTime":"2017-06-29T10:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T18:29:36.000Z","uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbfe589a619f4ca0894e164a540deca7e8bf4179","tid":302402,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001.html&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=359769c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170629175022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170629175022&h=bf0c29b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_02p.jpg?20170629175022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20170629175022&h=e7128091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_03p.jpg?20170629175022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20170629175022&h=6637e5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_05p.jpg?20170629175022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20170629175022&h=d60ab7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170629175022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170629175022&h=e3d52e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170629175022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629150141388-0629_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170629175022&h=81e540a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人陳瀅（Jeannie）和麥美恩（Mayanne）在主題公園活動中大騷長腿，其中Jeannie更以低裙吊帶裙亮相，甚有夏日氣息，之後她們把雙腳插在由沙堆成的魚尾中扮美人魚，非常有趣。<br />\n<br />\n胸圍在滑落狀態<br />\n<br />\n提到天氣炎熱，問Jeannie何以長時間搭一件外套在身上，兩女即笑不合攏，Mayanne忍不住大爆Jeannie的胸圍一直在滑落狀態，而Jeannie便尷尬認因着吊帶裙要戴粘貼式胸圍，但因為大汗而搞到甩Bra：「依家覺得好Free！」又謂習慣在家、在外國不戴Bra。<br />\n<br />\nMayanne即笑謂對方打一打眼色已經知咩事：「好彩我本身都冇乜本錢騷，大家今日平起平坐啦！」問她會否喜歡不戴Bra，她即笑指戴不戴也差別不大：「但我對自己身形有自信，平有平嘅好！」<br />\n<br />\n自爆在多倫多裸泳<br />\n<br />\n提到Jeannie在台上指自己小時候會玩裸泳，她即指小時候在多倫多家中的泳池裸泳，但在六歲搬走後沒有試過。與她讀同一間大學的Mayanne則指學校附近有天體沙灘，問她有否裸體埋一分，她即指自己只在入口偷望：「我發現得年紀大嘅人先做呢啲！」不過她坦言小時候會與哥哥一齊沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n問現在會否想試試裸泳，Jeannie即謂：「飲到非常醉，唔知自己做啲咩先會！」Mayanne則指想在婚前派對中與一班姊妹試試：「係Bucket List嚟嘅！」"},{"pid":"8fed87d6a6fa9faa09c72ab1c53e1da124385d8b","tid":302402,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7996f953e68c23cb3e892e15c14b465dfbc85647","tid":302402,"uid":7466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:04:36.000Z","msg":"啲雞味隔住個mon都聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":